sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Admin as Painel Admin
    participant API as API (/api/novo/users/[id]/approve)
    participant Auth as Auth Context (CASL)
    participant DB as Banco de Dados (Prisma)

    Admin->>API: POST /id/approve
    API->>Auth: Verifica se role == 'admin'
    Note over Auth: Se não for admin, retorna 403
    API->>DB: Busca usuário pelo ID
    API->>DB: prisma.user.update({ status: 'ACTIVE' })
    API-->>Admin: 200 OK (Usuário Ativado)
